data.text:
1 A New Ed

-------

Arise Ye, Ed

The Eds (Ed, Edd, and Eddy) takes a trip to a town called Springdale. They went to Mt. Wildwood to explore the forest, but they Discover a Cank-A-Kai. and freed a Yo-kai Whipser. Later they found Jibanyan using people for practice.

----------------------------------------------------------------------

The Eds along with their friends The Cul-De-Sac Kids (Rolf Jimmy, Nazz Sarah, and Kevin) Welcomes, Whisper, Jibanyan, Katie Forster, and her family by throwing a wild party unaware that Johnny and Plank plans to take his exact vengence on the Eds, and the Cul-De-Sac Kids.

A New Hope

--------------

Arise Ye Russian People

6 Revenge of the Ed Eddy's Brother has returned to the Cul-De-Sac. He's not alone, he has evil Yo-kai Dame Deadtime, Kin & Jin, and other Wicked Yo-kai to help him take revenge on Eddy. - Revenge of the Sith/Revenge of the Fallen
